data.description: "Absolutely spectacular, must-see home in a great neighborhood! This craftsmen style home boasts 2 new HVAC units and is located in a private community. Step onto the welcoming front porch for moments of relaxation and enjoy the gleaming wood floors throughout. The contemporary finishes and designer touches create a seamless flow from the kitchen, featuring quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances with views of the family room.     The main level also features a charming owner's suite. Every bedroom offers a sense of privacy, providing the ideal space to celebrate gatherings with family and friends. The upstairs landing features a workstation with desk and built-in shelving, adding functionality and style to the home. The private fenced backyard with pergola tops off the charm of this remarkable property. Make this gem yours today!"    Schedule to tour this home immediately! Interest rates are dropping and buyers are looking for the perfect place to call home. This could be it!!! Call your agent to view today!
